    <string name="dialog_about_message">
        Marks-Analyzer is an application created by students of Universitat Politècnica de València.
        It has been created with the unique objective of being shared with the rest of the students,
        in a non-interested way. UPV has not participated in any moment neither in the creation neither
        in the publication of this app, so <b>it is not an official app</b>.\n\n
        The login data will not be remembered unless you allow it, accesing menu Settings -> Privacy.
        Nevertheless, they are strictly necessary to access the documents which includes the marks.
        If you don\'t trust our application, please don\'t use it.\n\n
        If you have any sugerence, opinion or idea that could help our community, do not doubt to
